{"tid":1642874,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"雙十台灣連線注意","createTime":"2019-10-10T01:37:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T12:53:51.000Z","uid":296109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"742045878377bd2a74af964bbbdbb7f62c638982","tid":1642874,"uid":296109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T01:37:38.000Z","msg":"關於fing咩旗仔 同舉咩反共口號<br />\n之前已經 惹起過少少爭議<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔想再柒出國際/得罪人哋<br />\n唔該可唔可以全部花少少時間同我睇咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講述台灣戒嚴歷史 + 民主進化歷程<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mYSSQJEoGRU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmYSSQJEoGRU&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX5zDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=15cbefb3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mYSSQJEoGRU</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw好開心見到身邊啲人 雙十唔再係mon撚住個淘寶雙十節<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nP牌推唔郁 屌<br />\n今晚見<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f55A7Gv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff55A7Gv.jpg&h=fa58c6d8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tcap01v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTcap01v.jpg&h=ae73fae4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0AH4gzR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0AH4gzR.jpg&h=711ae32b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qgC0zmw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqgC0zmw.png&h=a986f7c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7ZMAoeS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7ZMAoeS.jpg&h=fccb14f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dcbc37a07557552c3ce73e2c0b0cd9460d20c196","tid":1642874,"uid":300554,"lik